title: Week 6 Waivers 2022
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp recap a historic MNF, give key injury updates, talk what we have learned after 5 weeks and what players’ stock is on the rise. Plus, Eric Moody joins to tell us who to target on the waiver wire.
